This file describes the directives and concepts tested by this test set.

test set name: smpmcpp02

directives:

  - _MPCP_Initialize()
  - _MPCP_Obtain()
  - _MPCPP_Release()
  - _MPCP_Get_ceiling_priority()
  - _MPCP_Set_ceiling_priority()

concept:

  
  - Ensure that a ceiling priority on MPCP semaphores works.
  - Ensure that a preemption of the normal execution by critical section works.
  - Ensure that a execution with two semaphores on the same processor works as expected.
  - Ensure that multiple obtain works for the MPCP
  
